{"word":"ἀγέλαστος","slug":"ἀγέλαστος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀγέλαστος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:γελάω'><el>γελάω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>not laughing, grave, gloomy, sullen</i>, <b>Hhymn.</b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <i>not to be laughed at, not trifling</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}